### UpdateName: Actual working one

PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/images/69aa55775d0055a033b181c0 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "updatedName"
}


### UpdateName: Too long name

PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/images/hi HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "loremdwaidwajkldwajdklwajdklwadwaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa"
}


### UpdateName: Missing name attribute

PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/images/hi HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "helloSilus": "loremdwaidwajkldwajdklwajdklwadwaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa"
}


### UpdateName: Invalid id

PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/images/hi HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "hi"
}


### Post password

POST http://localhost:3000/api/users HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "agustindimayuga@linux.com",
  "password": "password",
  "username": "agustinxocua"
}


### Post password repeat user error

POST http://localhost:3000/api/users HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "agustindimayuga@linux.com",
  "password": "password",
  "username": "agustinxocua"
}


### Post password

POST http://localhost:3000/api/users HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "agustindimayuga@linux.com",
  "password": "password",
  "username": "hello"
}


### Post invalid body

POST http://localhost:3000/api/users HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "doodle1": "agustindimayuga@linux.com",
  "doodle2": "password",
  "doodle3": "agustinxocua"
}


### Post Login Correct response

POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/tokens HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "password",
  "username": "agustinxocua"
}


### Post Login Wrong password

POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/tokens HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "password1",
  "username": "agustinxocua"
}


### Post Login Wrong username

POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/tokens HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "password",
  "username": "agustinocua"
}


### Post no username/password

POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/tokens HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "doodle1": "ehidhwiadhwiad",
  "doodle2": "fhjdksafhdjsklfdsjhkl"
